we.0: By selecting 'Submit', California residents can request to opt-out of the “sharing” of personal information with third parties for targeted advertising purposes, as defined by the California Consumer Privacy Act, where your personally identifying information is used. To opt out of cookie-based advertising, please see Your Privacy Choices Evidon. You can learn more about these rights by visiting our California Privacy Notice. If you exercise your right to opt-out of “sharing” personal information with third parties for targeted advertising, you may experience less targeted or personalized advertising, on other digital properties, that relate to Discover’s products and services. If you have enabled a tool that automatically communicates your opt-out preferences, such as Global Privacy Control (“GPC”), we will process the GPC signal as a request to opt out for the browser or device you are using at the time, so you may need to separately opt out on other browsers or devices that you use to visit our website.
